    "The most recent and old datasets for FD are described below, and they show the advantages and some limitations.Besides the datasets described in the previous table, there are some modern datasets used recently for detecting fraud attacks on credit card transactions that demonstrate distinguish benefits and some limitations, as follows:1.",
    "Dataset: Created in 2023, it contains credit card transactions by European card holders.",
